{"tid":225663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺仍對廣州/廣東有希望既人好天真","createTime":"2017-05-02T03:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T05:18:42.000Z","uid":84354,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15a71d6e28df40a7962296c5b9cd889811b47be3","tid":225663,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"以前成日聽到d人講咩廣州人都不滿個政權，甚至吹到廣州人都會幫香港人抗爭咁<br />\n屌啦 香港本身親建制/大中華既人都佔人口唔少 唔通廣州/廣東情況會好過香港？<br />\n佢地最多咪係某部分議題上反共，同埋排撈佬，講到尾咪又係愛國/愛國愛黨"},{"pid":"9654cbfe182f7091723491850b75a68161c6e8c7","tid":225663,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f307bac204bc826a8b43a2e4384a1b425df2d21e","tid":225663,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢地最多咪就係同我地文化相近"},{"pid":"e0ca767f0bc27d29a5239278cecb3611aae94903","tid":225663,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"屌埋廣東人依個潛在盟友對香港獨立有幫助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bee99b4820d23b3fd6557fd7b14b3c1f1aea2e","tid":225663,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌埋廣東人依個潛在盟友對香港獨立有幫助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人會係盟友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fe021f58bb249234afada7ee20aa8870614118","tid":225663,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"越撈越多北佬, 情況同香港相若"},{"pid":"56dbdccb8029eb7b2886e5711adc0453423a97c4","tid":225663,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌埋廣東人依個潛在盟友對香港獨立有幫助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人會係盟友？<img src